title: Arautos do Rei 50 Anos MP4
description:
The King's Heralds or Os Arautos do Rei is a Christian American origin with a focus on sacred music musical quartet. Was one of the pioneers of the musical style A Cappella. 

Was formed in 1927 under the name of The King's Heralds in the United States. They are recognized for their participation in the music program The Voice of Prophecy - one of the most famous and enduring radio-television programs of the USA and the world, in business for over 50 years. The quartet belongs to the music ministry of the Seventh-day Adventist Church.
